2. cs.MM (Multimedia): Person re-identification is also related to multimedia analysis and retrieval. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a deep feature fusion method and an adaptive re-ranking method, both of which involve machine learning techniques. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The proposed adaptive re-ranking method can be seen as a retrieval technique for person re-identification. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): Person re-identification has applications in security and surveillance, which may fall under this sub-category.
